<br />\n2021年4月29日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間14時50分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202104/29/P2021042900463.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202104%2F29%2FP2021042900463.htm&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=17d2bee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202104/29/P2021042900463.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"一巴車埋去啲唔讀書擦鞋仔度"},{"pid":"8096c52e9f08ef9cb5ed88241e70cb8e4c264938","tid":2509070,"uid":264887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"喺我唔忍喇入境處<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57895b2415c829a93333bf6003db1af248a3616","tid":2509070,"uid":199670,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50a1af338ef84c03a964341d526b0a7152208d0a","tid":2509070,"uid":282930,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"8ae2925c6aa7d515e0cb1ccc367f8504f545b5a0","tid":2509070,"uid":301952,"like":116,"dislike":3,"score":113,"quote":{"pid":"f6966ba5bb02a399e4c6821af27f45b640bae304","tid":2509070,"uid":39092,"like":187,"dislike":2,"score":185,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"入境班人以為曾國衛上左位就有人照<br />\n聲大大點知連基本野都唔識<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"擔心下審計署會比港共搞好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"審計署唔係同失咗蹤啲ICAC一樣，直接under 行政長官咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果係咁入境班人真係幾冇大冇細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"而家紀律部隊大晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":