br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2021年4月29日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間14時50分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202104/29/P2021042900463.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202104%2F29%2FP2021042900463.htm&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=17d2bee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202104/29/P2021042900463.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdaeade7d1e70884cd095a9afff34bdb82c85aa7","tid":2509070,"uid":43809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"無紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf738b885f321d45ee657400dec65b9e3c137da","tid":2509070,"uid":77180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99b789d9483d73d8b11ea0e9768ec90c2c478371","tid":2509070,"uid":130456,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"quote":{"pid":"50a1af338ef84c03a964341d526b0a7152208d0a","tid":2509070,"uid":282930,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"8ae2925c6aa7d515e0cb1ccc367f8504f545b5a0","tid":2509070,"uid":301952,"like":116,"dislike":3,"score":113,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"擔心下審計署會比港共搞好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"審計署唔係同失咗蹤啲ICAC一樣，直接under 行政長官咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果係咁入境班人真係幾冇大冇細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"根本就入境自己鳩<br />\n<br />\n審計署年年出報告 個個部門都會咬 洗咩急住仆出黎屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n差佬都俾佢咬車程同咪數唔岩啦 咪又係好好聲氣解釋 唔通又搵散仔會出黎屌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"年年都係回應會檢討會跟進就得架啦<i